### My Youtube-DL Configuration File

## Caching
--no-cache-dir  # do not use a filesystem cache

## Stream Selection
--no-playlist                   # if url points to video in playlist, only download the video
--prefer-free-formats           # prefer the use of free formats (obviously)
--format bestvideo+bestaudio    # download the best video stream and best audio stream, then merge them

## Post-Processing
--embed-thumbnail   # put thumbnail within the file as cover art
--embed-metadata    # put metadata within the file

## File Creation
--restrict-filenames    # only use ASCII, avoid whitespace
